Each [[Portfolio]] is steered by a [[squad|Autonomous Squad]] made up of its [[Product Leader]]s, [[Technology Leader]]s and [[Chapter Leader]]s. This squad's primary accountability is to factor and refactor the functional responsibilities of its portfolio's [[squads|Autonomous Squad]] by means of [[Portfolio Mapping]] and to enable the [[Portfolio Leader]] to intelligently liaise with their peers and the business's executives and HR.